para_trans: Mauje Bhood, Ta. Regarding sanction of new Sub-station at Khanapur, Dist. Sangli as a special case.
Government Decision No: Sub-Collector-2024 / P.No.245 / Health-4
Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Dispensaries), Mumbai: J. No.
Residence / Room 7A / T-9 / Ground / Sub-station / Approved / Sangli / 2676-78, dated 05.07.2024.
Preface: - Mouje Bhood, Ta. Health facilities to the residents of Khanapur, District Sangli
Since a new sub-station needs to be sanctioned in connection with the supply, a sub-station should be sanctioned at the site.
The matter was under the consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - Mouje Bhood, Ta. Approval for sanction of new Sub-station at Khanapur, Dist. Sangli as a "Special Matter"
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
